<paragraph id="B19E4FFAA724CBE5812C89201AEFADD3" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">Distribution</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0C5648EA136B24A1B5F9258825F53336" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">
Turkey, near Ankara (
<bibRefCitation id="E3AB58F3428E3015DC2F33032C13A363" author="Dlabola, Jiri" journalOrPublisher="Sbornik Narodniho Muzea v Praze, Řada B, Prirodni Vedy" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" pagination="173 - 248" refId="B7723741" refString="Dlabola, Jiri, 1980. Tribus-Einteilung, neue Gattungen und Arten der Subf. Issinae in der eremischen Zone (Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha). Sbornik Narodniho Muzea v Praze, Řada B, Prirodni Vedy 36 (4): 173 - 248" title="Tribus-Einteilung, neue Gattungen und Arten der Subf. Issinae in der eremischen Zone (Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha)" volume="36" year="1980">Dlabola 1980</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="D035B17705C5DDA3B3BF8A1593908E91" author="Kartal, V." journalOrPublisher="Doga Bilim Dergisi" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" pagination="99 - 103" refId="B7727564" refString="Kartal, V., 1985. Tuerkiye'den az bilinen Tshurtshurnella extrema Dlabola, 1980 (Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha, Issidae) tuerue. Doga Bilim Dergisi 10 (2): 99 - 103" title="Tuerkiye'den az bilinen Tshurtshurnella extrema Dlabola, 1980 (Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha, Issidae) tuerue" volume="10" year="1985">Kartal 1985</bibRefCitation>
) and Sinop (
<bibRefCitation id="292D0F8F5987D9985E326121FE9F2856" author="Tanyeri, Rukiye" journalOrPublisher="Sakarya University Journal of Science" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" pagination="594 - 600" refId="B7723732" refString="Tanyeri, Rukiye, Zeybekoglu, Uenal, 2021. Species of Cixiidae and Issidae (Hemiptera: Auchenorrhyncha: Fulgoromorpha) distributed in Sinop and Kastamonu (Turkey). Sakarya University Journal of Science 25 (2): 594 - 600" title="Species of Cixiidae and Issidae (Hemiptera: Auchenorrhyncha: Fulgoromorpha) distributed in Sinop and Kastamonu (Turkey)" volume="25" year="2021">
Tanyeri and 
<normalizedToken id="9879DFD90FD41A127A2BD43DD7B61D33" originalValue="Zeybekoğlu">Zeybekoglu</normalizedToken>
2021
</bibRefCitation>
)
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="93CC73DF8E7DF12A66AA6AA0F8F09ACD" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" type="notes">
<paragraph id="69AED3B67B09C41A724E397C28C85313" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1B68B9343E387DFD98084A5B0F2B5F4B" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">
First record for Bulgaria and Europe. 
<emphasis id="61D10C5BAC27CF6F9FA558E6A5AF1881" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">Eastern Sub-Balkan Basins</emphasis>
: Ajtos, 01.viii.2016, 2♂♂, 2♀♀ and 3 nymphs; (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="25AFCB4CB31E65AB91B8B86F93E67D0D" captionStartId="F7716874" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">7</figureCitation>
) on or near 
<taxonomicName id="82D14C12E7F4AD5B12D03F7B4988D262" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Astracantha" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Astracantha arnacantha subsp. aitosensis" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="arnacantha" subSpecies="aitosensis">Astracantha arnacantha subsp. aitosensis</taxonomicName>
(Ivan.) Reer &amp; Podlech. Detailed occurrence data: 
<bibRefCitation id="DEB8D135B5FF0CCE3336A35AF7F2BD57" author="Gjonov, I." journalOrPublisher="Annals of the Upper Silesian Museum in Bytom. Entomology" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" refId="B7727581" refString="Gjonov, I., 2022. new_fulgoromorpha_records_bulgaria_2022. In: Biodiversity Data Journal. Occurrence dataset." title="new _ fulgoromorpha _ records _ bulgaria _ 2022" volumeTitle="Biodiversity Data Journal. Occurrence dataset." year="2022">Gjonov (2022)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="519552D5A601790DB7B983104577DB9D" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">
<emphasis id="9EBB74213C15A887BDF3CC1167348AAF" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">Red Lists</emphasis>
: No assessment.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="888766E8337E4C6B78D522221D5F1664" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">
<emphasis id="0CA61FC3084AA400630DEB7D9ECAF01E" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">Host plant</emphasis>
: 
<taxonomicName id="45C9A5441F1043DAADCB40C079A80C17" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Astracantha" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Poaceae</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation id="89AB359ABB3ED83B2DE1364DD69690F5" author="Dlabola, Jiri" journalOrPublisher="Sbornik Narodniho Muzea v Praze, Řada B, Prirodni Vedy" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" pagination="173 - 248" refId="B7723741" refString="Dlabola, Jiri, 1980. Tribus-Einteilung, neue Gattungen und Arten der Subf. Issinae in der eremischen Zone (Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha). Sbornik Narodniho Muzea v Praze, Řada B, Prirodni Vedy 36 (4): 173 - 248" title="Tribus-Einteilung, neue Gattungen und Arten der Subf. Issinae in der eremischen Zone (Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha)" volume="36" year="1980">Dlabola 1980</bibRefCitation>
). All specimens reported here were collected on 
<taxonomicName id="B84F828AF22F5E31B0C9D0410DEFC878" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Astracantha" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Astracantha arnacantha subsp. aitosensis" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="arnacantha" subSpecies="aitosensis">Astracantha arnacantha subsp. aitosensis</taxonomicName>
or near it.
</paragraph>
